---
title: Creamy Shrimp Soup with Broccolini and Celery
description: Inspired by cioppino, a hearty Italian-American shellfish stew, this velvety seafood soup is enhanced by a mix of tangy-sweet roasted red pepper pesto and luscious cream. Juicy shrimp seasoned with paprika and garlic get a touch of heat from a sprinkle of red pepper flakes.
